variants.Description in input context: Wild-type (WT) R-syn and mutant A53T R-syn

Material used.Description: Differentiated SH-SY5Y cells overexpressing WT or A53T R-syn.

Readout description.Result Description: Protein expression levels were analyzed using 2-D DIGE.

Technical replicates.Description: Each sample was run in triplicate.

Basic positive control.Description: Host vs WT and host vs A53T comparisons were used as controls.

Statistical analysis method.Statistical analysis method: ANOVA was used for statistical analysis, followed by independent t-tests.

Threshold for normal readout.Threshold for normal readout: Protein expression levels within the range of WT cells.

Threshold for abnormal readout.Threshold for abnormal readout: Protein expression levels significantly different from WT cells (p < 0.05).
